  "story": {
    "beat": "Dusk over a windswept clifftop village that has feared the mountain for a hundred years. Elder Mara begs Jim to end the curse before the last seal breaks.",
    "narration": [
      "The ferryman dropped me at the docks of Halward's Reach. A strange quiet hangs over this place.",
      "They say the mountain watches. I'm here to find out why."
    ]
  },
